  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为物流仓库系统设计一个状态流转图，核心是从入库到出库的全流程。初始状态应该是Absence，也就是货物尚未登记的状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Absent",
        "Инициализация"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以起点是Logistics_Warehouse触发初始化进入Absent。那扫描操作作为状态转换的触发条件，我们用\"Start\"和\"End\"来区分入库和出库扫描对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Сканирование",
        "Start",
        "End"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。正常流程是：扫描\"Start\"从Absent进入CheckedIn（已入库），然后扫描\"End\"进入Attended（已处理）。但这里有个关键点——如果货物在Absent状态就被扫描\"End\"，这是异常操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这种异常应该导向Error状态。我注意到这个错误和Logistics_StockLevel有关，可能是库存数据不匹配导致的。另外，Error状态需要能重置回Absent吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "Сброс / Очистка ошибки"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，要有重置路径。还有几个边界情况：CheckedIn状态下如果再次扫描\"Start\"，应该保持CheckedIn，这对应Logistics_Warehouse的重复确认；Attended状态下无论扫描\"Start\"还是\"End\"，都保持Attended，关联Logistics_StockLevel的最终确认。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我来绘制这个状态图。起点Logistics_Warehouse，状态包括Absent、CheckedIn、Attended、Error，转换条件都标注扫描操作和关联模块。Error旁边我会加一个注释说明这是Nekorrektnoe deystvie（错误操作），关联Logistics_TrackingNumber。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "stateDiagram-v2",
        "note right of Error",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，Attended的自循环条件我写错了——应该是\"Start\"或\"End\"都可以，不是\"и\"连接。还有Error的注释，用俄语描述错误操作类型，但模块名Logistics_TrackingNumber保持英文。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Attended -- Attended",
        "note right of Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已修正。现在Attended的自循环是\"Сканирование 'Start' или 'End' (Logistics_StockLevel)\"，Error注释为\"Некорректное действие (Logistics_TrackingNumber)\"。整个状态图v2版本完成了，需要再检查哪个转换条件吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "stateDiagram-v2",
        "Attended",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题了，所有路径都覆盖了：正常入库出库、重复扫描保持、异常扫描进入错误、错误重置。可以定稿。",
      "elements_involved": [
